{"word":"G1641 - ἐλαττονέω - elattonéō - el-at-ton-eh-o - Have lack","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐλαττονέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">elattonéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">el-at-ton-eh-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have lack</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - குறையப்பண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to be less, inferior (in possessions)"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1640 - ἐλάσσων - elássōn - el-as'-sone/1640\">G1640</a>; to <i>diminish</i>, that is, <i>fall short:</i> - have lack.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}